"msg":"津路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d215240af6f40fd9667276b4fe542ec171661d6","tid":2041073,"uid":69975,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"之前都試過，試過睇下佢地行去邊<br />\n發現原來可能有啲嘢食/糖(特別係溶左嘅)會吸引佢地<br />\n掉咁啲嘢抹乾淨就會開始少"},{"pid":"276ba8802314f4455353226f2ae7629486b3f297","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"網購左螞蟻絕 要等幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說放左威滅幾日了 都無咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b32ebedb6f0c7d9fdaa3855b40040bf4479038","tid":2041073,"uid":106524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"我之前間房都有<br />\n我係用漂白水噴(無稀釋)<br />\n佢哋第一下聞到會停一停唔敢行<br />\n隔一陣會有一兩隻出黎探路<br />\n之後我一見到有就噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴左幾次就無曬"},{"pid":"2eaf3ab1fa1d116c1deab8df31abd80e01bba5a6","tid":2041073,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276ba8802314f4455353226f2ae7629486b3f297","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"網購左螞蟻絕 要等幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說放左威滅幾日了 都無咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣用殺他死都OK，群群蟻唔同，唔一定食你嗰隻藥"},{"pid":"a43ca342bdbfec295c59a14b8612018887bbefa2","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"83b65ff48b30dd3710bda6c4d77667e914ca17ea","tid":2041073,"uid":195438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a43ca342bdbfec295c59a14b8612018887bbefa2","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"慢慢嚟啦，嗰陣我第一次發現係由我門框搬去冷氣機，之後搞掂兩邊就發現廁所門框有，之後廚房電制，騎樓門框，廚房牆裂痕，又落藥又封死晒，搞咗一大輪依家先叫好似消失晒"},{"pid":"02e16885ed92ff6581ba4a70ea611e5630472026","tid":2041073,"uid":60410,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:35:09.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<br />\n唔係害蟲就由佢啦"},{"pid":"174dbbad6c22b30abac28f77caefed1f7ea41323","tid":2041073,"uid":303977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:44:36.000Z","msg":"㩒死完蟻 即刻用番梘水抹乾淨<br />\n啲蟻死咗會留低氣味引其他蟻過嚟<br />\n我瀨過嘢第二朝半間房係蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22503ad0fd95fde5f25785eaf0cc2275c96fa6e4","tid":2041073,"uid":12929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"42d4a46e521cbf761805b9383a04da689eb39db9","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"前日開始間房突然好多蟻, 之前明明咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企廁所本身有蟻, 而我間房同廁所好近, 諗緊會唔會係班蟻走左去我間房到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知點整走d蟻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚴重影響我生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用左威滅一日 但好似都無咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:51:40.000Z","msg":"Amazon 搵呢隻蟻膠，啲蟻會食完之後帶番去餵蟻后食，最係死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用法: 沿住蟻路每隔1 -2m 滴少少，啲蟻會圍住佢黎食，情況可能好誇張，但由得佢地食飽番屋企。兩三日後就唔會再見到啲蟻㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91%2BWuPMXUVL._AC_SY450_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91%252BWuPMXUVL._AC_SY450_.jpg&h=1ac24e04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67a8e1089751a4f01417f0c5d65dc551abc5f136","tid":2041073,"uid":12929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:54:21.000Z","msg":"無咗圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/TERRO-Liquid-Ant-Killer-T200/dp/B0015031R8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTERRO-Liquid-Ant-Killer-T200%2Fdp%2FB0015031R8&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33GXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=b67edc5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/TERRO-Liquid-Ant-Killer-T200/dp/B0015031R8</a>"},{"pid":"e00d7d36c3bc7f1015752c16c501cf2ab5fc6090","tid":2041073,"uid":12929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:55:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0B1qvELzcTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0B1qvELzcTI&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33GXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=cb83b0b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0B1qvELzcTI</a>"},{"pid":"88650602ff8a699b963d795db07317a1e22c830a","tid":2041073,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T22:57:52.000Z","msg":"以後唔好係房食任何有糖分嘅嘢 擺都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千奇唔好係房用誘捕器 佢地會拉大隊一齊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誘捕器放番係廁所好啦"},{"pid":"ee3d612fdf3d6f02efa4903aad2474ca32a555cf","tid":2041073,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"屌 做乜鳩無啦啦成屋都多左蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3f43b57e56fe48fc054bc6989d0f53f3b144e1","tid":2041073,"uid":276508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82d439d6a21e7d1500ad1f64391046194f82930","tid":2041073,"uid":318220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"到爽身粉落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"硅藻土粉會唔會好d？<br />\n據說咩蟲都殺到+無抗藥性"},{"pid":"be63f896da0f45807c54453dba0327735be5072e","tid":2041073,"uid":73374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T23:32:34.000Z","msg":"係藥房買硼砂，一個火柴盒咁大，幾蚊包，返到去用1:1硼砂溝糖+一兩滴水，攪勻佢，hi係佢平時會出沒嘅牆度。唔使理佢哋佢哋會食，同埋運返佢哋個竇度，最後成家都會死晒。<br />\n<br />\n唔使成包溝晒，我果時用左一茶匙咁多到，因為驚難抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前屋企都有，好核突，佢哋係會有一條平時行開嘅路徑，應該因為有味，我試過用消毒火酒抹左佢哋條路徑，之後佢哋就亂鳩咁行囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03d3ea03f3a9b024ffde0ec9d28546340f92d3a","tid":2041073,"uid":73374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82d439d6a21e7d1500ad1f64391046194f82930","tid":2041073,"uid":318220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"到爽身粉落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T23:34:32.000Z","msg":"試過爽身粉，佢地大部份會避開行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係有一兩隻on9仔撞左入去死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668dceabf47fd2b926b9bf4bf1ae3e611358285e","tid":2041073,"uid":204755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T23:53:46.000Z","msg":"我同樓主一樣情況，而家連飲水機同杯都間唔中有螞蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全搞唔掂"},{"pid":"55a53510f0e192b01435607bd427ba72e5